"W2_Q88"	"Variable Label"	"Q88. EU SCENARIOS"
"W2_Q88"	"1"	"Carrying on, with only small and incremental progress in the deepening of European integration."
"W2_Q88"	"2"	"A shift of focus towards market integration between EU countries only."
"W2_Q88"	"3"	"Emergence of a multi-speed EU, in which selected countries cooperate and integrate more closely than others."
"W2_Q88"	"4"	"Focus on deeper integration amongst all EU countries in a limited number of areas, such as in foreign policy and defense"
"W2_Q88"	"5"	"EU countries integrate more deeply than ever before across policy areas, resulting in the European Union becoming a fede"
